metadata.name: Cherry lipstick
metadata.description:
I'm ready to present you the first photo from "Amylee" collection.
Artworks that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

Some come to the bar to relax after a hard day, some come to mourn heartbreak, and Amylee comes to have a good time. Cherry lipstick is a constant attribute of her evening.

Photo: 4008x6000 px
